那就把條件加在 VERIFY..BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT 上。

如果你的驗證邏輯是：

1. 找出純新光戶 (Flag=1 且沒有 2/3)
2. VERIFY 的 IsSARFiled = 1
3. 比對 BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT 的 IsSARFiled 是否相同

SQL：

WITH CUST_LIST AS
(
    SELECT TS_CUST_ID
    FROM BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO
    WHERE CUST_RE_NO_FLG = '1'
    EXCEPT
    SELECT TS_CUST_ID
    FROM BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO
    WHERE CUST_RE_NO_FLG IN ('2','3')
)
SELECT
    c.TS_CUST_ID,
    CAST(v.IsSARFiled AS INT) AS VERIFY_IsSARFiled,
    CAST(b.IsSARFiled AS INT) AS BSA_IsSARFiled,
    CASE
        WHEN ISNULL(CAST(v.IsSARFiled AS INT),0)
           = ISNULL(CAST(b.IsSARFiled AS INT),0)
        THEN 'Same'
        ELSE 'Different'
    END AS CompareResult
FROM CUST_LIST c
INNER JOIN VERIFY..BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT v
    ON c.TS_CUST_ID = v.CustomerNo
LEFT JOIN BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT b
    ON c.TS_CUST_ID = b.CustomerNo
WHERE v.IsSARFiled = 1
ORDER BY c.TS_CUST_ID;

如果你只想看有問題的：

...
WHERE v.IsSARFiled = 1
  AND ISNULL(CAST(v.IsSARFiled AS INT),0)
      <> ISNULL(CAST(b.IsSARFiled AS INT),0);

理論上如果資轉正確，這批客戶應該都是：

TS_CUST_ID	VERIFY_IsSARFiled	BSA_IsSARFiled	CompareResult
xxx	1	1	Same

而最後那支「只看差異」的 SQL 應該回傳 0 筆。這就是最好的驗證結果。 ✅